comment_data.body: See line 1275 for the counterpart that needs to be changed as well.
If this ever fails, it's a hard bug (nothing outside the code influences this - it should never fail), so we should probably at least log an error here.
I'll start a list of things we need to log once the logger is added to the DHT code
